    Point-of-Sale and Barcode
















The Channel’s Leading Point-of-Sale and Barcode Solutions

ScanSource POS and Barcode offers automatic identification and data capture (AIDC) and point-of-sale (POS) solutions from many of the industry’s leading manufacturers. In addition, resellers are able to utilize any of the number of value-added services available to them, including sales and technical support, education and training, custom configuration, marketing support, financing services, design support, installation, rollouts and many others.
 
ScanSource POS and Barcode Business Units include:


ScanSource POS and Barcode, US/Canada 
ScanSource POS and Barcode, Europe

ScanSource Latin America (Miami)
ScanSource Mexico
ScanSource Brazil



 






















