    Communications
















The Industry’s Most Comprehensive Communications Solutions

ScanSource offers communications solutions in two of its business units, ScanSource Catalyst and ScanSource Communications.  Through these sales units, resellers have access to voice, video, mobility, network security and data equipment from many of the industry’s leading manufacturers.  In addition, resellers are able to utilize any of the number of value-added services available to them, including sales and technical support, education and training, marketing support, financing services, design support, installation and many others.
 
ScanSource Communications Business Units include:


ScanSource Communications, US/Canada 
ScanSource Catalyst, US/Canada 
ScanSource Communications, Europe
ScanSource KBZ
ScanSource Latin America (Miami)
ScanSource Mexico
ScanSource Brazil



 































