    Physical Security
















Industry-Leading Physical Security Solutions

ScanSource Security is a value-added distributor of the industry’s leading physical security solutions. ScanSource Security exclusively serves the reseller community and is committed to never competing with its dealer or reseller partners. In addition, the distributor provides education and training opportunities that can help resellers expand their knowledge of IP physical security products and solutions. ScanSource Security also brings a variety of value-added services that allow resellers to focus on sales and customer service, including custom configuration, technical support, state-of-the-art logistics, financial services, and marketing support – not to mention products in stock and ready to ship from a centralized location.

ScanSource Security Business Units include:

ScanSource Security, US/Canada 
ScanSource Latin America (Miami)
ScanSource Mexico



 






















