    Products
















Delivering Essential Solutions through IP Products & Unmatched Customer Service

ScanSource Networking and Security is proud to now stock and sell Pelco by Schneider Electric. They are a company that truly understands that information is critical to success, which is why they are singularly focused on the development of video surveillance and security solutions that provide users the information necessary to make real-time, business-enabling decisions.
From the recently introduced VideoXpert video management platform, to their industry-leading fixed and high-speed IP cameras (panoramic, thermal imaging, explosion-proof and more), Pelco offers a camera for any environment, any lighting condition, and any application.  Pelco offers the broadest selection of IP cameras designed for security surveillance in a wide variety of commercial and industrial settings, with an unparalleled level of customer support and services.  

For more information about how ScanSource can help you with your Pelco business, please reach out to the 
Product Manager, Jessica Samuels, or your ScanSource Networking and Security sales rep today! 














